    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2 in concours-level condition. This specimen retains its original F22C1 2.2L longitudinal DOHC VTEC powerplant, delivering linear power delivery to a factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers short-throw precision with no synchro grind. The chassis remains structurally pristine, preserving the legendary X-bone frame rigidity and double-wishbone suspension geometry. All body panels retain matching VIN tags, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation or fluid seepage. A turn-key example for the purist seeking peak analog performance.",
